definitions: TALK FROM MEMORY/Hungira motjiuru. TALK IN RAGE/Hungira nomazenge. - LIKE A FOOL/nyoma(o). - TOGETHER/Hungira pamwe.
THE FOOD TASTES NICE/Ovikurya mavi tjata nawa.
THANK YOU/okuhepa. THANK YOU FOR THE BREAD/Okuhepa komboroto.

word: THE GENTLE ONE, THE TAME ONE

definitions: -/-ngande. - PORRIDGE/Oruhere orukande, otjisema (ovi-). PORRIDGE, FOOD/onguma. - FAT/Omaze omakande.
I THINK I SHALL COME/Me tjangovasi kutja me ya.
HE SPOKE THE TRUTH THROUGHOUT/Eye wa hungire ouatjiri ongazu.
THE HORSE THREW THE PERSON/Okakambe ka nata omundu.
DO NOT - DOWN THE WOOD, PUT IT DOWN GENTLY/O yeme orukune, twa pehi katiti.
THE HORSE THROWS YOU/Okakambe make ku huku.
